U.K.’s Carbon Trust Names Ex-Shell Chief James Smith as Chairman

-- B y   A l e x   M o r a l e s
-- 
2011-09-26T11:01:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/u-k-s-carbon-trust-names-ex-shell-chief-james-smith-as-chairman.html
The U.K.’s Carbon Trust, which
advises businesses on carbon reduction, named former Shell U.K.
chairman  James Smith  as its chairman, the group said today in an
e-mailed statement. Smith replaces Ian McAllister, who is
stepping down after a decade, the trust said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
